      ]
    },
    "node_007": {
      "id": "node_007",
      "speaker": {
        "name": "旁白",
        "color": "#aaaaaa"
      },
      "text": "走进教室，我看到一个女孩子正独自坐在窗边，望着窗外的樱花发呆。",
      "background": "@/assets/galgalme/background/272a3819eccb400f6e7dd6a74f03c0d3e389f7b6.jpg",
      "characters": [
        {
          "characterId": "sakura",
          "position": "left",
          "expression": "neutral",
          "visible": true
        }
      ],
      "transition": "slide",
      "edges": [
        { "id": "e_007_008", "type": "auto", "target": "node_008" }
      ]
    },
    "node_008": {
      "id": "node_008",
      "speaker": {
        "name": "小樱",
        "color": "#f472b6",
        "characterId": "sakura"
      },
      "text": "（察觉到视线，转过头来）……啊，你好。你也是这个班的吗？",
      "background": "@/assets/galgalme/background/272a3819eccb400f6e7dd6a74f03c0d3e389f7b6.jpg",
      "characters": [
        {
          "characterId": "sakura",
          "position": "left",
          "expression": "surprised",
          "visible": true
        }
      ],
      "edges": [
        { "id": "e_008_009", "type": "auto", "target": "node_009" }
      ]
    },
    "node_009": {
      "id": "node_009",
      "speaker": {
        "name": "旁白",
        "color": "#aaaaaa"
      },
      "text": "我注意到她的桌上放着一本厚厚的植物图鉴。",
      "background": "@/assets/galgalme/background/272a3819eccb400f6e7dd6a74f03c0d3e389f7b6.jpg",
      "characters": [
        {
          "characterId": "sakura",
          "position": "left",
          "expression": "smile",
          "visible": true
        }
      ],
      "edges": [
        {
          "id": "e_009_010",
          "type": "choice",
          "label": "「你喜欢植物吗？」",
          "conditions": [],
          "target": "node_010"
        },
        {
          "id": "e_009_011",
          "type": "choice",
          "label": "「你就是传说中的图书委员？」",
          "target": "node_011",
          "conditions": [
            { "type": "flag", "key": "met_hiyori", "operator": "eq", "value": true }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    "node_010": {
      "id": "node_010",
      "speaker": {
        "name": "小樱",
        "color": "#f472b6",
        "characterId": "sakura"
      },
      "text": "嗯！我最喜欢樱花了。你知道吗？樱花的花语是「精神之美」和「纯洁」。",
      "background": "@/assets/galgalme/background/272a3819eccb400f6e7dd6a74f03c0d3e389f7b6.jpg",
      "characters": [
        {
          "characterId": "sakura",
          "position": "left",
          "expression": "happy",
          "visible": true
        }
      ],
      "onEnter": [
        { "key": "sakura_affection", "value": 2 },
        { "key": "met_sakura", "value": true }
      ],
      "edges": [
        { "id": "e_010_end", "type": "auto", "target": "node_end" }
      ]
    },
    "node_011": {
      "id": "node_011",
      "speaker": {
        "name": "小樱",
        "color": "#f472b6",
        "characterId": "sakura"
      },
      "text": "诶？你怎么知道的？……是日和告诉你的吧？那孩子总是到处宣传……",
      "background": "@/assets/galgalme/background/272a3819eccb400f6e7dd6a74f03c0d3e389f7b6.jpg",
      "characters": [
        {
          "characterId": "sakura",
          "position": "left",
          "expression": "blush",
          "visible": true
        }
      ],
      "onEnter": [
        { "key": "sakura_affection", "value": 1 },
        { "key": "met_sakura", "value": true }
      ],
      "edges": [
        { "id": "e_011_end", "type": "auto", "target": "node_end" }
      ]
    },
